Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:33.98,ed-trans,,0,0,0,,I noticed the scent of summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:41.49,JP_ED-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ひしめく光が照らす
