Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:41.69,ed-trans,,0,0,0,,and the crowded, shining lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:48.71,JP_ED-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}想いに耳を澄ませば
